The '''Pella Compact''' was the council that led the first settlers to the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Pelagon]] in the [[Tapani sector/Legends|Tapani sector]] approximately [[13,000 BBY]]. It continued to govern the colonies for around a thousand years before power was devolved during the [[Twelve Kingdoms Era]]. It initiated the first contact with the [[Herglic/Legends|Herglics]].

